    "id": "webizen-pro"
  }, "Webizen Pro"), mdx("p", null, "The concept of Webizen Pro: is that it is a specific Hardware / Software Specification, that is designed to provide 'Artificial Intelligence' (term used broadly) capabilities that are designed to operate in a particular way.  In-effect, this provides some insights / description of the concept described of as 'webizen', that in-turn provides far greater value than any of its parts alone."), mdx("blockquote", null, mdx("p", {
